Package: leaveprob
Type: Package
Title: Calculates Probability of Manager Leaving via Resignation vs. Termination
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Heather Handy
Maintainer: Heather Handy <heatherhandy@wafflehouse.com>
Description: This package calculates the probability of a manager leaving by resigning or by being terminated from the position.
    A probability around 0.5 indicates approximately equal chance of resigning or being terminated. A value closer to 1.0 indicates higher 
    chance of resigning. A value closer to 0.0 indicates higher chance of being terminated rather than resigning.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
Imports: devtools, readxl
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
